  <li class="li5"><p><strong>Submission Payment &mdash;</strong> Submission to the festival is $11 USD. In rare circumstances, the submission fee can be waived due to proven financial need &mdash; please contact <a href="mailto:info@fronterasmicrofilm.com">info@fronterasmicrofilm.com</a> with the subject line &ldquo;Fee Waiver&rdquo; for more information.</p></li>
  <li class="li5"><p><strong>Eligibility &mdash; </strong>Fronteras Micro-film Festival (the &ldquo;Festival&rdquo;) is open to human beings of Earth eighteen (18) years of age or older at the time of submission. Void where prohibited. In order to submit the Festival, you must fully comply with the Official Rules and, by entering, you represent and warrant that you agree to be bound by these Official Rules and the decisions of the Sponsor, whose decisions shall be binding and final in all respects relating to this Festival.</p></li>
  <li class="li5"><p><strong>Timing &mdash; </strong>Festival submission begins March 1, 2023 at 4:00 PM Mountain Standard Time and ends May 2, 2023 at 11:59 PM Mountain Standard Time (&ldquo;Festival Submission Period"). Administrator is the official time keeper for the Festival Submission Period. The Festival is governed by these Official Rules and is subject to all applicable federal, state, provincial and local laws.</p></li>
  <li class="li5"><p><strong>How to Enter &mdash; </strong>During the Festival Submission Period, there are two methods to enter a film for selection (&ldquo;Submission&rdquo;):<br />
  <ol class="ol1">
    <li class="li5" id="portrait"><p>For 9:16 films (&ldquo;Portrait Films&rdquo;), upload the video to TikTok with the hashtag #FronterasMicrofilm, then go to <a href="https://fronterasmicrofilm.com">https://fronterasmicrofilm.com</a>&nbsp;and complete the online submission form by providing your First Name, Last Name, Email Address, Date of Birth, Payment Information and TikTok link. Submission for the Portrait Films category must not exceed 60 seconds (1 minute) in length and must be submitted in 9:16 format.</p></li>
    <li class="li5" id="other"><p>For all other film categories, go to <a href="https://filmfreeway.com/Fronterasmicrofilmfestival">https://filmfreeway.com/Fronterasmicrofilmfestival</a> and upload your film, then submit to the appropriate category. For 16:9 category, the submission must not exceed 180 seconds (3 minutes) in length and must be submitted in 16:9 format. For 4:3 category, the submission must not exceed 90 seconds (1.5 minutes) in length, must be silent, must be black and white, and must be submitted in 4:3 format. For all submissions, credit sequences count toward the total length of the film.</p></li>
  </ol>
  <p>Limit of five (5) Submissions per person for the Festival, throughout the entire Festival Submission Period. Entrants may only use one email address to submit the Festival. Use of any automated system to enter is prohibited and will result in disqualification. Sponsor is not responsible for lost, late, incomplete, invalid, unintelligible or misdirected entries all of which will be ineligible to be selected by the Festival. In the event of a dispute as to any entrant, the authorized account holder of the email address used to enter will be deemed to be the entrant. The "authorized account holder" is the natural person assigned an email address by an Internet access provider, online service provider or other organization responsible for assigning email addresses for the domain associated with the submitted address.<p>
