  <li class="li5"><p><strong>Winner Determination &mdash; </strong>After the end of the Festival Submission Period, a panel of qualified judges determined by Sponsor in its sole discretion (collectively, &ldquo;Festival Judges") will select the best Submissions for each category (the "Finalists") from among all eligible Submissions that were submitted, based on an equal application of the following criteria:<br /></p></li>
  <ul class="ul1">
    <li class="li5"><p>Creativity/Originality (50%)</p></li>
    <li class="li5"><p>Relevance to the stated themes of the Festival (25%)</p></li>
    <li class="li5"><p>Relevance to the installations (25%)</p></li>
  </ul>
  <p>In the event of any tie at any phase of the judging, the entrant who receives the higher score in the "Creativity" category, as determined by the Festival Judges in their sole discretion, will be selected from among the tied entrants as the potential Finalist. Odds of winning depend on the number of eligible entries received during the Festival Submission Period and the quality of the Submissions.</p>
  <p><strong>ON OR ABOUT MAY 9, 2023, FINALISTS WILL BE CONTACTED USING THE EMAIL ADDRESS OR PHONE NUMBER PROVIDED WITH THE SUBMISSION AND WILL BE REQUIRED TO RESPOND WITHIN THREE (3) DAYS OF NOTIFICATION VIA EMAIL AND MAY BE SELECTED SUBJECT TO VERIFICATION AND ELIGIBILITY AND COMPLIANCE WITH THESE TERMS OF THE OFFICIAL RULES.</strong></p>
